    <div class="content"><p><a href="http://www.arcscience.com/OmniGal.htm" rel="nofollow">OmniGlobe</a></p>
<p>I have a feeling I have seen mention of other such projects on a bigger scale, but a quick Google turned up that commercially available 2 meter one.</p>
</div>
