    <h3 class="title"><a href="/node/405#comment-4204" class="active">That one looks cool</a></h3>    <div class="submitted">Submitted by <a href="/user/brad" title="View user profile." rel="nofollow">brad</a> on Sat, 2007-07-14 13:17.</div>
    <div class="content"><p>That's very close.  It doesn't appear to have a nightside.   There are arguments for and against that.  Nightsides are more realistic of course but then people can only see certain parts of the Earth when the museum is closed.  It seems to use panels which would be higher resolution, but not give the image of looking at the planet from space.</p>
