    <div class="content"><p>The Delorme map company has a giant photorealistic rotating globe, though admittedly not real-time, in their lobby. They call it <a href="http://www.delorme.com/companyinfo/eartha.htm" rel="nofollow">Eartha</a>, and will sell you one of your own if you have a few million to spare. Shame about the poor-quality PDF sales brochure.</p>
