    <div class="content"><p>I just finished reading Jpod and when I googled dglobe to see if it was gonna happen, I got a link to this page, of course. I searched it because it's a pretty great idea. Since I read the book I've been thinking about how much one might cost; I'd buy one but, couldn't you pretty much do the same thing on a computer these days? But still, a computer is not a globe, and it'd be one pretty groovy globe.</p>
